We are based in Montreal - Canada and we work with a team of collaborators worldwide. We were united by our shared affection of mobile gaming; what a great way to make friends! While we celebrated the good times spent playing together, we also commiserated over games we found repetitive as well as the fact that game producers kept ignoring great ideas for improving those games, so we did the sensible thing and decided to create the ultimate game all of us would enjoy playing!Quantum is a real time mobile Massively Multiplayer Online Role Playing Game (MMORPG) where your mission is to rebuild our civilization after an alien attack and seventy years of occupation have left us depleted. The weekly cooperative events will allow you to test your strength and defenses, and give you the opportunity to pursue and conquer the invaders and overcome the different challenges this harsh planet will throw at you. On a personal level, since you’re an inhabitant of an irradiated and contaminated world, you’ve started to experience strange, yet positive changes; we chose to call them Quantum Abilities. Let’s see how you can master those!What makes Quantum extra-special is the Feedback System we are putting in place so that all the players of the Quantum community can shape the storyline and the features of the game. You will find more details about the Feedback System and other features in our video, and a bit below.Our goals with the Indiegogo CampaignWe’re thrilled about this campaign because:1) It gives us an opportunity to let you know about Quantum and show you a little bit of what to expect from the game. We hope to create a great fan base so that, when the game launches, we will already have a big crowd of eager players ready to get into the action and make the events even more exciting to participate in!2) It gives you the opportunity to start participating in the development process right away. That’s right! As we go along, you'll be kept in the front row and your input will be solicited so that you can influence some of the developmental decisions before Quantum is launched!3) We want Quantum to make it onto your devices as soon as possible. Even though the design process and programming of the game have already started, we need your financial support to complete the project. There are also some fees to cover in order to launch Quantum and its integrated Feedback System. Here is the cost breakdown at a glance:ChallengesThis is our first foray into the mobile game world; we are very aware of this. This is why we are being uber-careful and working extra hard to make sure we deliver a unique experience paired with a high quality product. What we may lack in raw experience in the field of game production, we make up for with massive amounts of passion for this project and the strongest of work ethics. We will achieve this because we surrounded ourselves with those we consider the best people to get the job done in a high quality fashion. Therefore, we feel 100% confident of our success; we sure hope you will get on board with our great adventure!How to participate in the success of this campaignTo thank you for supporting the project, we have set up some pretty cool rewards! Make sure to choose wisely as they will give you a great head start when you play the game. On top of this, the 100 first contributors will get extra rewards.Here is a table to compare the different Packs.Also: Share! Share! Share! Every tiny little bit of sharing using the Indiegogo tools is a great help for the campaign and you will be rewarded accordingly through our referral program (more information below). So, please let your family and friends know about the project and participate in the Team Challenge for a chance to get additional rewards! These are ways to ensure that, together, we make this campaign a success!Thanks a million for your support! The Team at Atomic Cloud StudiosYou need more details to make a decision?You've come to the right place! Here is all you will want to know. Here is a bit more about what to expect from Quantum.Storyline and environmentIn the year 2026, a vicious alien attack resulted in unprecedented levels of devastation on Earth. Humans have been hiding underground, barely surviving the alien occupation for the past seventy years. Quantum is the story of how we, the survivors, decide to fight back for our world.In this first chapter of the game, From the Rubble, the alien aggression has left us with a harsh, rusted world. Luckily, plenty of leftover items and goods can be found in the rubble and are up for grabs; we will find these nifty items pretty useful to arm ourselves against the invaders. Moreover, the aliens may have left behind the key to their own destruction in the form of advanced alien technology which we will use to improve and hybridize our own weapons and skills. The opportunity to change the course of mankind’s future is waiting to be discovered, hidden in the ruins of our fallen civilization.Various weekly events
Spy missions (infiltration, extraction, sabotage, kidnapping, etc.);
Invasion/Occupation Wars; 
Misfortunes and disasters: biological hazards, natural catastrophes, artificial intelligence gone rogue, and more!
Personal Hero and Army
8 base items of equipment to choose from, each one variable and upgradable to strengthen your Hero;
8 different Quantum Abilities for special powers with spectacular effects;
Ground, Motorized and Air Forces to fight alongside with;
And Special Creatures too!
Partnership
Team up with other players and build a strong Partnership;
Worldwide coalition to beat the game in a cooperative manner;
Leaders' elaborate dashboard during events for an efficient use of strategy and easy management;
Players’ history to show achievements and contributions.
Other
Defense: Defense Crew, Buildings and other technologies;
Utilities: Coach, Builders, Looters, Strategists, etc.
Facilities: Resources, Space management (housing, parking, wildlife center), Academy (to train your army), Research facilities (military, genetics, etc.)
For us, there is nothing more inspiring than the many suggestions and ideas enthusiastic players make regarding the enhancement of a game. This is why the Feedback System is an important component of Quantum.The fully integrated Feedback System will include:A) A voting system where you will be able to decide on what rewards we should offer next, some components of the events coming up, the implementation of different ideas suggested by the players community, the direction the story should be heading in, etc.B) Forums where you will be able to provide suggestions and, in collaboration with other players, improve on those suggestions so that we can make those ideas become a reality in the game.C) A fan fiction space and contests to inspire the direction the story and the following stages of the game should take.  D) Live events with the creators/producers of the game.E) Anything else you might be inclined to suggest that we’re capable of bringing to life!We can't wait to hear what you have to say! To thank you for sharing the campaign information, we will reward you with 15% (in-game Premium Currency) of the value that your friends contribute to the campaign.For example, if you share the campaign using the Indiegogo sharing features and a bunch of your friends connect to the platform using your link and contribute a total of 1,000$, you will receive 150$ worth of in-game premium currency. Make sure to use the Indiegogo sharing features as this way, we can track all the donations linked to you. Getting loads of rewards is exciting and we can't wait to distribute them to you! We want to make sure that you are 100% happy with your rewards when you get them; this is why transparency is very important to us so you know what you are getting into.Here is the detailed information you need to know and understand about the perks.In-Game Premium CurrencyFirst, please note that the Premium Currency value is the only item amongst the rewards that is cumulative and can be merged into a single account.  Unless we inform you otherwise, for the purpose of this campaign, the Premium Currency worth will be calculated this way: 1 unit = 1 USD cent value. For example, if you choose the Partner Pack (110$ Perk), you will receive 150$ worth of in-game premium currency, which will translate to 15,000 units.Name in the CreditsThe game’s website will feature a page displaying the names of all the contributors (Crew, Partner and Hero Packs). If you prefer to remain anonymous, you will be able to let us know when the time comes. Supporter Account BadgeThis will be a special badge that will be displayed in your game account to let everybody know that you directly contributed to the success of the game’s development. If you don't want it to appear, you will be able to turn it off.Quantum Ability PointsYou will be able to boost your Quantum Abilities (QA) as you choose in order to give yourself an edge. You could choose to be a specialist with a particular QA boosted to the max, or distribute your points between the eight QA. These points, like all good things, have to be earned and can only be won by participating in fun, yet challenging events. Please note that you can upgrade an ability to its maximum level by using 100 QA pointsSpecial in-game itemsIf the perk you choose includes receiving a character or a defense unit, you will receive them at the promised level. Please take note that you won’t be able to upgrade them further until you are at the appropriate level to do so (it will be the same level as all the other players). Nonetheless, having those items right from the start will give you a huge head start in the game, so we hope you will enjoy them greatly! Please have a look at this table to know more about when an item unlocks and is made available in the game.  Also, the items you will receive count as the first one(s) as the game unfolds. For example, there are five towers that are gained through the different HQ upgrades in the game. If your pack offers you one tower, then it counts as the first unlocked tower in the game. You’ll have to wait until you reach the appropriate level to get a second one (the same level all the players get to build two towers). The good thing is that you won’t have to use in-game resources to build it, nor will it require your precious builders’ time to do so.Tickets to Atomic Cloud Studios ConventionsThese tickets will give you access to the activities for the whole duration of the convention. VIP tickets will grant exclusive access to special activities.You will be able to redeem the tickets for the year and location of your choice. You can decide to redeem the tickets one at a time in order to attend multiple conventions (up to the number of tickets included in your perk), or you can share them with friends.  Please note that accommodations, transport, etc., are not included; we offer only the tickets to enter the convention(s).Participation in the testing of Quantum
When the time comes, we will give you more details about this participation. It will be your responsibility to comply with the terms at that time so you can get into the testing events.Prototype Live DemoYou will have access to a live demonstration of the game prototype.Creative session with the design teamThis will be an hour-long virtual session with our design team so you can pitch a few of your ideas and brainstorm with us. Your opinion could also be solicited about an upcoming event, for example. This session could (or not) be followed up with a few other meetings to fine-tune the concepts and details. We will let you know if that is the case. Of course, not every idea can be produced exactly as imagined, but we will do our best to make your idea come to life, keeping in mind that it will need to be in line with the vision and theme of the game.Customized AvatarIn collaboration with our design team, you will create a unique and exclusive avatar for yourself. Some limitations (pornographic content, racist content, etc.) may apply.Follow-up information request and distribution of the rewardsAt a date still to be determined, you will receive a request for more information so we can gather all the necessary details needed to deliver the perks.Our team will work relentlessly so that you can get your rewards as soon as we can distribute them. You will be responsible for providing us with the information in a reasonable time, and to follow our instructions to retrieve your rewards. DelaysWe aim to distribute the rewards as soon as the game is released so that you can enjoy them right away. If the release of the game ends up being delayed due to unfortunate circumstances, then the distribution of the rewards will be too. This is not the plan, though! Let's keep this project on track, and we will keep you informed every step of the way! ***Wow! Very first achievement – reading through all of this! Congrats! :)The Team at Atomic Cloud Studios
